OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FHeavy rain soon clearing to
OL,6,Fthe east to leave a largely dry day
OL,7,Fwith some bright spells and just the
OL,8,Fodd isolated shower. Light winds
OL,9,Fstrengthening in the evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fwith heavy outbreaks of rain Sunday.
OL,13,FSunny spells and a few showers on
OL,14,FMonday. Dry with sunny spells Tuesday.
OL,15,FStrong winds and risk of gales Sunday,
OL,16,Fthen becoming light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
